http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: This article lists Internet television providers – broadcasters of Internet television using digital distribution – by region and by country. Internet TV is typically transmitted wirelessly, or through hard-wired devices, via an over-the-top programming platform to enabled SmartTVs, set-top-boxes, personal computers, smartphones, tablet computers, and digital media receivers.
